<emphasis bold="true" box="[912,934,1929,1955]" italics="true" pageId="184" pageNumber="185">♂</emphasis>
Fuhsing, Taiwan. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1152,1173,1928,1954]" pageId="184" pageNumber="185">A</emphasis>
